title: DAC7578 Breakout Front and Back Comparison
summary: Side-by-side product photo of the board front and back. The rear side includes printed electrical details such as default I2C address and supply range.

structured_data.description: Left image shows populated front side with IC and connectors; right image shows back side silkscreen with text 'Default I2C Addr 0x4C', 'Broadcast Address 0x47', and 'VLogic/Vcc: 3-5VDC'.
